-- Alliance Data to buy Conversant for $2.3 bln
-- By Amrutha Gayathri in Bangalore
-- Thu Sep 11, 2014 04:13PM EDT
-- None



Sept 11 (Reuters) - Credit card processor Alliance Data Systems Corp <ADS.N> said it will buy digital marketing company Conversant Inc <CNVR.O> for about $2.3 billion in cash and stock.

Alliance Data will acquire Conversant for $35 per share. The deal is expected to close by year end. [ID:nPn7ppjyT]